message.body: I ended up with a bus ticket for 1pm - do you want to come over at 10:30 for breakfast? And we can just catch up? I am so sorry - i am a bit over scheduled this week.
No worries!! I have had a crammed week as well. Yeah I'll stop by at 10:30 with some treats!
We can have a quick bite and coffee.
Or we can postpone for next week!
I'll be back Friday night late so yes!
Oh great! Yeah - lets plan on meeting in that Saturday! I will also be back Friday night - 10:3o then - I can commit to working till 2:30
Awesome. Sounds good. I will see you then and have a fun weekend and safe bus ride.
Perfect! I am glad that worked out - I hate rushing! Have a lovely weekend!
Thanks for always bring flexible - I do want to get back on a routine with you this winter!
Me too it's the worst. See ya!
Back atcha. After The holidays we are on!
